This is the natural 2ct correct buy — exactly as the 1ct G-VS2 is the 1ct correct buy. The 2ct Commitment (a 410% price increase for 1.6mm additional diameter) is a real market structure, not a judgment. Within this commitment, G-VS2 GIA Excellent is the only defensible choice. Spending $22,460 for E-VVS2 or $26,490 for D-VS2 buys invisible grade premiums on a stone that already commands attention at 8.1mm.

The all-in ring at this tier: $16,490 stone + $900–$1,500 platinum 6-prong solitaire = $17,390–$17,990. For $18,000–$20,000 total, you can add a pavé band or cathedral setting at this size.

